Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: Unicorn fails to generate payloads

Verify Metasploit is properly installed: msfconsole --version
Check Python version: python3 --version (should be 3.6+)
Ensure proper permissions on /opt/unicorn directory
Issue: ClamAV not detecting EICAR test file

Update virus definitions: sudo freshclam
Restart ClamAV daemon: sudo systemctl restart clamav-daemon
Verify EICAR string is exact (no line breaks or modifications)
Issue: Python scripts fail with import errors

Install required packages: pip3 install requests
Verify Python path: which python3
Check script permissions: chmod +x script_name.py
Issue: Payloads detected at high rates

Try additional obfuscation layers in advanced_obfuscation.py
Implement variable name randomization
Add more junk code and time delays
Test with different payload types (HTTPS vs TCP)
